positiveProductReview.reviewDescription: Everything is good about this iPhone except its Price :( People out there waiting for this iPhone including me from a very long time but unable to buy this due its over-price. I hope Apple India will realise this and soon bring its price down and will see some happy customers :) Cheers to those who are enjoying there brand new iPhone 6s (y)
